                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Conger</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Hay</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram—Paraphase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Pekin</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1900-10-01">
                            <hi rend="italic">October 1, 1900</hi>
                        </date> (via Taku, October 5).</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>(Mr. Conger acknowledges receipt on September 30 of Department’s telegram of
                    September 22 communicating replies to Chinese, Russian, and German
                    Governments.)</p>
            </div>
